      • locate

        public static TypeLibInfo locate(GUID libid,
                 String version)
                          throws BindingException
        Locates the type library file from the LIBID (a GUID) and an optional version number.
        Parameters:
        libid - String of the form "xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx"
        version - Optional version number. If null, the function searches for the latest version.
        Throws:
        ComException - If it fails to find the type library.
        BindingException
